- Always try to use the available shacdn components instead of creating new components
- Try to use the colors of the colors palette, primary and secondary 
- Always group the import in "components", "utils", "types" or "services"
- When creating new components or functions, always use named exports with arrow function syntax whenever possible:

DO THIS:
export const ComponentName = () => {
  // implementation
}

export const functionName = () => {
  // implementation
}

DON'T DO THIS:
export default function ComponentName() {
  // implementation
}

function functionName() {
  // implementation
}
export default functionName;